---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Harga & Paket Layanan — Epigrap" 
  description="Pilihan paket berlangganan sistem portal phygital Epigrap untuk ranah personal, pariwisata, hingga enterprise."
>
  <div class="pricing-page-wrapper">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="pricing-header text-center">
      <h1 class="brand-title">PILIHAN <span class="text-brass">HARGA</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Investasi untuk keabadian digital tanpa batas waktu maupun ruang.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Info Note -->
    <div class="disclaimer-banner container">
      <div class="disclaimer-box">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <path d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <p>Seluruh harga pada halaman ini merupakan biaya lisensi <strong>sistem digital Epigrap</strong> (portal, CMS, dan infrastruktur). Untuk pembuatan monumen fisik seperti prasasti, plakat, atau tugu, Anda dapat bekerja sama langsung dengan <a href="/partner" class="inline-link">jaringan mitra pengrajin</a> kami dengan tarif terpisah.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing Cards -->
    <section class="pricing-cards-section container">
      <div class="cards-grid">
        
        <!-- Tier 1: Privat -->
        <article class="price-card card-dark">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h2 class="tier-name">Privat & Keluarga</h2>
            <p class="tier-target">Untuk Silsilah, Memori Keluarga & Makam Pusaka</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="price-box">
            <div class="price-setup">
              <span class="currency">Rp</span>
              <span class="amount">1.500.000</span>
            </div>
            <p class="price-label">Biaya Setup Awal (Termasuk Masa Aktif 1 Tahun Pertama)</p>
          </div>

          <div class="price-renewal">
            <p><strong>Rp 300.000</strong> / tahun (mulai tahun ke-2)</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Pembuatan 1 Portal Monograf</li>
            <li>Generate QR Code Digital (Siap Cetak)</li>
            <li>Penyimpanan Cloud Memori Keluarga</li>
            <li>Galeri Silsilah & Audio Memorial</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/dasbor" class="btn-cta btn-outline">Reservasi Sistem</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Tier 2: Publik -->
        <article class="price-card card-dark">
          
          <div class="card-header">
            <h2 class="tier-name">Pariwisata & Publik</h2>
            <p class="tier-target">Untuk Candi, Wisata Religi & Monumen Kesenian</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="price-box">
            <div class="price-setup">
              <span class="currency">Rp</span>
              <span class="amount">4.500.000</span>
            </div>
            <p class="price-label">Biaya Setup Awal (Termasuk Masa Aktif 1 Tahun Pertama)</p>
          </div>

          <div class="price-renewal">
            <p><strong>Rp 1.200.000</strong> / tahun (mulai tahun ke-2)</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Pembuatan Portal Wisata & Ruang Publik</li>
            <li>Fitur Audio Naratif Multibahasa</li>
            <li>Fitur Donasi & Penjualan Produk Digital</li>
            <li>Analitik Scan Pengunjung & Peta Interaktif</li>
            <li>Dukungan Update Konten</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/dasbor" class="btn-cta btn-fill">Reservasi Sistem</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Tier 3: Enterprise -->
        <article class="price-card card-dark">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h2 class="tier-name">Enterprise</h2>
            <p class="tier-target">Untuk Gedung Pemerintah, Pabrik & Korporasi Besar</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="price-box custom-price">
            <div class="price-setup">
              <span class="amount-text">Kustom</span>
            </div>
            <p class="price-label">Disesuaikan berdasarkan kerumitan infrastruktur</p>
          </div>

          <div class="price-renewal">
            <p><strong>Berbasis SLA</strong> (Kesepakatan Tahunan Fleksibel)</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li>Portal Aset & Peresmian Berskala Besar</li>
            <li>Pengembangan API Kustom & Integrasi Sistem</li>
            <li>Lisensi Deployment On-Premise (Opsional)</li>
            <li>Arsitektur Berstandar Global</li>
            <li>Dukungan Teknis Prioritas</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/dasbor" class="btn-cta btn-outline">Hubungi Konsultan</a>
        </article>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Blockchain Add-On Section -->
    <section class="blockchain-section container">
      <div class="blockchain-wrapper">
        <!-- Decorative blockchain network visualization -->
        <div class="chain-visual">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 600 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="chain-svg">
            <!-- Connecting lines (right edge to left edge of next cube) -->
            <line x1="50" y1="30" x2="150" y2="30" class="chain-line"/>
            <line x1="190" y1="30" x2="280" y2="30" class="chain-line"/>
            <line x1="320" y1="30" x2="420" y2="30" class="chain-line"/>
            <line x1="460" y1="30" x2="550" y2="30" class="chain-line"/>

            <!-- Cube 1 -->
            <g class="chain-cube" style="--cube-delay: 0s">
              <polygon points="30,25 30,55 10,45 10,15" class="cube-left"/>
              <polygon points="30,25 50,15 50,45 30,55" class="cube-right"/>
              <polygon points="10,15 30,5 50,15 30,25" class="cube-top"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Cube 2 -->
            <g class="chain-cube" style="--cube-delay: 0.6s" transform="translate(140,0)">
              <polygon points="30,25 30,55 10,45 10,15" class="cube-left"/>
              <polygon points="30,25 50,15 50,45 30,55" class="cube-right"/>
              <polygon points="10,15 30,5 50,15 30,25" class="cube-top"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Cube 3 (center) -->
            <g class="chain-cube" style="--cube-delay: 1.2s" transform="translate(270,0)">
              <polygon points="30,25 30,55 10,45 10,15" class="cube-left"/>
              <polygon points="30,25 50,15 50,45 30,55" class="cube-right"/>
              <polygon points="10,15 30,5 50,15 30,25" class="cube-top"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Cube 4 -->
            <g class="chain-cube" style="--cube-delay: 1.8s" transform="translate(410,0)">
              <polygon points="30,25 30,55 10,45 10,15" class="cube-left"/>
              <polygon points="30,25 50,15 50,45 30,55" class="cube-right"/>
              <polygon points="10,15 30,5 50,15 30,25" class="cube-top"/>
            </g>

            <!-- Cube 5 -->
            <g class="chain-cube" style="--cube-delay: 2.4s" transform="translate(540,0)">
              <polygon points="30,25 30,55 10,45 10,15" class="cube-left"/>
              <polygon points="30,25 50,15 50,45 30,55" class="cube-right"/>
              <polygon points="10,15 30,5 50,15 30,25" class="cube-top"/>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="blockchain-content">
          <h2 class="blockchain-title">
            <span class="text-brass">Keabadian On-Chain</span> — Fitur Tambahan
          </h2>
          <p class="blockchain-headline">
            Server bisa mati. Perusahaan bisa bangkrut. <strong>Tapi blockchain tidak pernah padam.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="blockchain-desc">
            Epigrap adalah satu-satunya platform portal phygital yang menawarkan opsi <strong>pencatatan permanen</strong> ke jaringan blockchain terdesentralisasi. Setiap konten — foto, teks, audio, video — yang sudah Anda unggah ke portal dapat diabadikan secara on-chain, sehingga <strong>tidak bisa dihapus, diubah, atau dimanipulasi oleh siapapun, selamanya.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="blockchain-tech-grid">
          <!-- Arweave -->
          <div class="tech-card">
            <div class="tech-card-header">
              <span class="tech-badge">STORAGE LAYER</span>
              <h3 class="tech-name">Arweave</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="tech-desc">Penyimpanan data permanen. Bayar sekali, tersimpan selamanya di jaringan terdesentralisasi yang tersebar di seluruh dunia. File asli Anda — bukan hanya tautannya — benar-benar hidup di blockchain.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Polygon -->
          <div class="tech-card">
            <div class="tech-card-header">
              <span class="tech-badge">PROOF LAYER</span>
              <h3 class="tech-name">Polygon</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="tech-desc">Sertifikat bukti keabadian. Setiap konten yang di-mint akan dicatat sebagai bukti kepemilikan digital (on-chain proof) yang dapat diverifikasi oleh siapapun melalui blockchain explorer publik.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How it works -->
        <div class="blockchain-how">
          <h3 class="how-title">Bagaimana Cara Kerjanya?</h3>
          <div class="how-steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <strong>Top-Up Kredit</strong>
                <span>Isi saldo kredit minting melalui dashboard Anda.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-divider"></div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <strong>Pilih Konten</strong>
                <span>Tentukan file mana yang ingin diabadikan secara on-chain.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-divider"></div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <strong>Minting Otomatis</strong>
                <span>Epigrap mengeksekusi pencatatan ke Arweave & Polygon. Anda terima bukti transaksi.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="blockchain-note">
          <p>✦ Fitur ini bersifat <strong>add-on</strong> dan tidak termasuk dalam paket langganan di atas. Biaya minting ditentukan berdasarkan ukuran file dan kondisi jaringan saat transaksi. Tersedia untuk semua tier paket.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .pricing-page-wrapper {
    padding-top: 10rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top center, rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.05) 0%, var(--color-obsidian) 70%);
  }

  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: fadeDown 1s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .brand-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .text-brass {
    color: var(--color-brass);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.7);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Disclaimer Banner */
  .disclaimer-banner {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease-out 0.2s forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .disclaimer-box {
    background: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.2);
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.5);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .disclaimer-box svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .disclaimer-box p {
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.7);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .disclaimer-box strong {
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.9);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: var(--color-brass);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .inline-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Cards Grid */
  .pricing-cards-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  /* Individual Card */
  .price-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease, border-color 0.4s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease-out 0.4s forwards;
  }

  .price-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .price-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

  .price-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .card-dark {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .card-highlight {
    background: rgba(30, 27, 20, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(197,160,89,0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.1);
  }
  .card-highlight:hover {
    border-color: rgba(197,160,89,0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.15);
  }

  .popular-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-brass);
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tier-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tier-target {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Price Area */
  .price-box {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .price-setup {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .currency {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.8);
  }

  .amount {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
  }
  
  .amount-text {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .price-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .price-renewal {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .price-renewal p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.7);
  }

  .price-renewal strong {
    color: var(--color-parchment);
  }

  /* Features */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes button to bottom */
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.8rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0px;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    border: 1px solid rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.3);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-fill {
    background: var(--color-brass);
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-brass);
  }
  .btn-fill:hover {
    background: var(--color-parchment);
    border-color: var(--color-parchment);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.3);
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(300px, 450px);
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .disclaimer-box {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  /* =============================================
     BLOCKCHAIN ADD-ON SECTION
     ============================================= */
  .blockchain-section {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease-out 1s forwards;
  }

  .blockchain-wrapper {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(30, 27, 20, 0.6), rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8));
    border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Subtle glow effect behind the wrapper */
  .blockchain-wrapper::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .chain-visual {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .chain-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .chain-line {
    stroke: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.25);
    stroke-width: 2;
    stroke-dasharray: 6 4;
    animation: chainFlowLine 2s linear infinite;
  }

  /* 3D Cube faces */
  .cube-top {
    fill: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.35);
    stroke: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.5);
    stroke-width: 0.5;
  }

  .cube-right {
    fill: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.15);
    stroke: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.4);
    stroke-width: 0.5;
  }

  .cube-left {
    fill: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.08);
    stroke: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.35);
    stroke-width: 0.5;
  }

  .chain-cube {
    animation: cubePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: var(--cube-delay);
  }

  @keyframes chainFlowLine {
    0% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
    100% { stroke-dashoffset: -20; }
  }

  @keyframes cubePulse {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.5;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 0px transparent);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.4));
    }
  }

  .chain-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .blockchain-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .blockchain-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .blockchain-headline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .blockchain-headline strong {
    color: var(--color-brass);
  }

  .blockchain-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .blockchain-desc strong {
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.9);
  }

  /* Tech Cards (Arweave & Polygon) */
  .blockchain-tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .tech-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.8rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tech-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.25);
  }

  .tech-card-header {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    background: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.1);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .tech-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
  }

  .tech-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* How it works */
